    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the sale of fireworks to protect animals",
        "additional_details": "I've had to bring my horses back from a horrendous 10 mins of horror, my mare run into a wooden fence when I had to put her out along with my pony he hasn't been well since. \r\n\r\nThis all happens to wildlife also, there's sheep in lamb in the fields around us, the fireworks can make these farm animals abort their young. Horses die because of the stress, I've had this mostly every year for 10 years, enough is enough.",
        "background": "Demand a complete ban on fireworks, animals are dieing because of them.\r\nWe're still commiting atrocities against animals and no one is doing any thing about this, they have rights in this world too.",
